
                              RbVisa

  Ruby wrapper around National Instrument visa library.
  Allows easy scripting for control of your favorite oscilloscopes

  author      hugo benichi
  email       hugo [dot] benichi [at] m4x [dot] org
  copyright   2012,2013 hugo benichi
  homepage    http://github.com/hugobenichi/rb_visa

  Installation:

    run "rake gem_install" from the /rb_visa root directory to install the gem
    in your ruby gem directory.

    rb_visa assumes that the National Instrument drivers are already installed
    on your system.

  Usage:

    see examples scripts in /rb_visa/test/
